  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perhaps we have never escaped our fate.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/3c470b95c415c399ee8aff35f4f56e4c.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=92 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/3c470b95c415c399ee8aff35f4f56e4c.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/b9d663c1862b50bf383a18da85c32963.webp?t=1766996811\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/b9d663c1862b50bf383a18da85c32963.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" class=\"bb_img\" width=144 height=144 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/3c470b95c415c399ee8aff35f4f56e4c.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=92 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/3c470b95c415c399ee8aff35f4f56e4c.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Xi\" is a horror puzzle game set in the context of modern Chinese folklore.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story takes place in a long-abandoned mountain mansion. This immersive escape room experience feels a bit too real, with eerie and strange elements everywhere—an empty banquet, an endless corridor, and you, who have accidentally stumbled into this haunted house. Can you really escape? Fortunately, there are others in the mansion; unfortunately, they don't seem to be human... Who is telling the truth? I can't tell, I really can't tell...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/c7cd83b215da29cd028d76cd4fcb0be5.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/c7cd83b215da29cd028d76cd4fcb0be5.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/cd05cf14e13c1f6cb9ac8b5f8bd3a538.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/cd05cf14e13c1f6cb9ac8b5f8bd3a538.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/d934ebfc8faf979589053556167cabab.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/d934ebfc8faf979589053556167cabab.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/cdb58ceaa1bb5daa6759d5291d032c24.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/cdb58ceaa1bb5daa6759d5291d032c24.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/eea4a9a05463ddf0f0a68c40a427c760.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/eea4a9a05463ddf0f0a68c40a427c760.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/f1de39d22216e5a5ab15365206ad9b1f.avif?t=1766996811\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras_big/f1de39d22216e5a5ab15365206ad9b1f.avif?t=1766996811 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       A purchased girl is betrothed to a ghost? Is this another story of feudal remnants persecuting young girls? No, no, no, the truth this time might be simpler than you think. A neo-Chinese pixel art style recreates the eerie mansion of a wealthy family in the early Republic of China era. As a staunch materialist, I don't believe in any supernatural beings. I have strength and strength... uh... and occasionally some wisdom. No matter what, can you really calm the resentment of the ghost bride, save her soul, and make it out alive? But... who is the one that really needs saving?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.apng?t=1766996811\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" class=\"bb_img\" width=19 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>A unique adventure of \"Jing Xi\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece together the vanished past and discover a story that belongs to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.apng?t=1766996811\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" class=\"bb_img\" width=19 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>A classic pixel-style RPG game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No cliché jump scares, just pure Eastern mysticism. Feel the mysterious power of the East!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four endings in total, with one being the official true ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.apng?t=1766996811\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/e1cedc4ac45182dba021a4dd5913e302.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" class=\"bb_img\" width=19 height=50 /></picture></span><strong>Intricate ancient-style ensemble.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character in the game has their own agenda. Uncover the secrets behind the characters—there might be a chance to break through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/12c9332bedfd569912c189cff1cb2117.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=800 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/12c9332bedfd569912c189cff1cb2117.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't rest yet; there are monster girls wandering outside (♪Legend of Chaos♪ plays here).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/b1efee9b09eab3970586dda5e62cf547.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=624 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/b1efee9b09eab3970586dda5e62cf547.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/b1efee9b09eab3970586dda5e62cf547.mp4?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About other game content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Working on it, working on it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/d473c92e89eb061e80c16ebd8c01009c.webp?t=1766996811\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/d473c92e89eb061e80c16ebd8c01009c.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" class=\"bb_img\" width=155 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I heard that if you slack off, a mysterious force might take you away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/c1a55c5313307a50fdd6822baa53d62a.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=240 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/c1a55c5313307a50fdd6822baa53d62a.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                   Follow us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                          Please, we beg you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/83aa01ad790a70a6e51a76a6a9b19680.poster.avif?t=1766996811\" width=79 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432160/extras/83aa01ad790a70a6e51a76a6a9b19680.webm?t=1766996811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
